name: LEVIATHAN
description:
An ever expanding 3D sculpture.

A new sculpture is generated every day containing 1 more cube than the previous day.

Day 1 = 5 January 2022.

Original artwork by Herman Pretorius, 2022.

Made with JavaScript (no dependencies).

Homepage: https://www.sizeight.com/
Social: @sizeight

Hot keys
========
SPACE / Left click = Pause
F = Forward 1 frame
B = Back 1 frame
W = Speed up
Z = Slow down
M = Show / hide meta info
P = Toggle size (Browser size / Print size, 2048 × 2048 px)
